[thinking] **Considering Testcontainers metadata**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about the implications of generating metadata for Testcontainers. It seems problematic because the TCK user-code-filter is limited to just org.neo4j.driver, but the classpath includes Testcontainers. I wonder if native images might require testcontainers' reachability if tests are using it. This makes me think it might be safer to avoid using Testcontainers altogether in native images. It’s important I get this right to prevent any complications!
[thinking] 
[thinking] **Preparing for Graph Database**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering that meaningful coverage of GraphDatabase.driver/session/query requires a live Neo4j setup. The runtime dependencies appear to be self-contained, so no extra Maven dependencies are needed. I should take action to prepare for this advisory. It’s important to ensure that the JSON is valid, without any newline issues. Ultimately, I want to end up with a final, single JSON object only to maintain clarity.
[thinking] 
